name: NIGHTMARES - PART 2
description:
The horned skeleton shedding blood is a rather dramatic piece that reflects on the countless animals being killed in the laboratory, forest fires, hunting and other humane means of causing chaos.

I plan to do a more in-depth series on this soon.


_


Tools: Cinema 4D, Realflow, Octane Render and Photoshop.

Res: 1080 x 1080px

Format: .mp4
